parameters:
General Atu: I apologize for making you come all the way to
a place like this.

General Atu: It's becoming increasingly difficult to
accommodate them in just the Camps' prison.

Thief Nora: Does that mean the battles in the Camps have
intensified...?

General Atu: It has become a problem not only in the Camps,
where the military has started to take action, but
throughout the entire empire.
Thief Nora: P-Please! I have comrades, important comrades!

Thief Nora: We're not the kind of bad people you all think
we are--

General Atu: What you all say may be true, but they are
thieves.

General Atu: They are enemies of the empire, disrupting the
order of the empire.

Thief Nora: No... I don't want that. Everyone... the
captain... will be killed.

Clea: Why are you taking such drastic measures against the
Camps?

General Atu: There is also political manipulation by
Pido... but the spread of a drug called Dragon's Tears is
the main cause.

General Atu: There may be good thieves and bad thieves, but
war encompasses all of them.

General Atu: I have a request for all of you. I want you to
carry out the subjugation of the remnants who fled to the
treacherous marshland.
Thief Nora: ...No, I don't want to, I can't do it.

General Atu: If you refuse, even though I have settled the
matter with Agonia, I will simply ask someone else.

General Atu: It's just a thought... but the injured members
of the Emma Thief Guild have taken refuge in the treacherous
marshland.

General Atu: I have decided to believe all of your reports
regarding [what happened to them].

Clea: Nora, let's go to the treacherous marshland right
away.
Thief Nora: Yes... we have to rescue as many as possible!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Campus Region / Treacherous
Marshland\c[0]
